@page "/"
@inherits AppComponentBase

<div class="home-bg">
    <section class="page-sec to-the-moon">
        <div class="sec-body">
            <div class="sec-title">To the Moon</div>
            <div class="sec-subtitle">through the Clouds.</div>
            <div class="sec-desc">Bit Platform is a digital innovation company with software development at its core. We help out our customers innovate with designing and building their digital products efficiently with our Agile mindset and lean processes.</div>
            <a class="sec-btn--primary" href="/cases">See Our Showcases</a>
        </div>
        <div class="sec-bg"></div>
    </section>
</div>

<section class="page-sec what-we-offer">
    <div class="sec-title">WHAT WE OFFER</div>
    <div class="sec-title-underline"></div>
    <div class="sec-content">
        From IT strategy consulting and comprehensive technology roadmaps to the end-to-end development of scalable solutions, Bit Platform delivers a full-cycle software development services that adapt seamlessly to your project requirements and business needs.
    </div>
    <div class="sec-card-group">
        <a href="/services#solutions" class="card card-1">Web development</a>
        <a href="/services#solutions" class="card card-2">Mobile development</a>
        <a href="/services#solutions" class="card card-3">Consulting services</a>
        <a href="/services#solutions" class="card card-4">Artificial intelligence</a>
        <a href="/services#solutions" class="card card-5">UI/ UX design</a>
        <a href="/services#solutions" class="card card-6">Technical support</a>
        <a href="/services#solutions" class="card card-7">Cloud base solutions</a>
        <a href="/services#solutions" class="card card-8">Game development</a>
    </div>
    <a class="sec-btn--primary" href="/services">Explore More</a>
</section>

<div class="success-bg">
    <section class="page-sec success-story">
        <div class="sec-title">OUR SUCCESS STORIES</div>
        <div class="sec-title-underline"></div>
        <div class="sec-content">
            Your story will go up there.
        </div>
        <div class="sec-carousel">
            <BitCarousel Class="carousel" ShowNextPrev="false" InfiniteScrolling="true" @ref="_carouselRef">
                @foreach (var showCase in Cases)
                {
                    <BitCarouselItem>
                        <div class="slide">
                            <img class="slide-image" src="/images/home/MacBook Pro 16 inch.png" alt="@showCase.Name" />
                            <div class="slide-content">
                                <div class="slide-title">@showCase.Name</div>
                                <div class="slide-title-underline"></div>
                                <div class="slide-desc">@((MarkupString)showCase.Description)</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </BitCarouselItem>
                }
            </BitCarousel>
        </div>
        <div class="prev-next">
            <button @onclick="() => _carouselRef!.GoPrev()">
                <svg fill="none" width="56" height="56">
                    <path d="M28 49.0004C39.598 49.0004 49 39.5984 49 28.0004C49 16.4024 39.598 7.00037 28 7.00037C16.402 7.00037 7 16.4024 7 28.0004C7 39.5984 16.402 49.0004 28 49.0004Z" stroke-width="2" stroke-miterlimit="10" />
                    <path d="M26.6656 35.4159L19.25 28.0003L26.6656 20.5847" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
                    <path d="M19.25 27.9999H36.75" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
                </svg>

            </button>
            <button @onclick="() => _carouselRef!.GoNext()">
                <svg fill="none" width="56" height="56">
                    <path d="M28 49.0004C39.598 49.0004 49 39.5984 49 28.0004C49 16.4024 39.598 7.00037 28 7.00037C16.402 7.00037 7 16.4024 7 28.0004C7 39.5984 16.402 49.0004 28 49.0004Z" stroke-width="2" stroke-miterlimit="10" />
                    <path d="M29.3345 35.4159L36.7501 27.9999L29.3345 20.584" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
                    <path d="M19.25 27.9999H36.75" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
                </svg>
            </button>
        </div>
        <a class="sec-btn--primary" href="/cases">See Our Showcases</a>
    </section>
</div>

<section class="page-sec how-we-work">
    <div class="sec-title">HOW WE WORK</div>
    <div class="sec-title-underline"></div>
    <div class="sec-content">
        We employ best practice processes and development methodologies as a foundation for rapid building of cutting-edge technology solutions in a structured and methodical way.
    </div>
    <div class="process-card process-card-1">
        <div class="process-card-title">Functional Specification</div>
        <div class="process-card-desc">This is the initial step in the development process where the goals and requirements of the project are defined and a map is created to guide the development process.</div>
        <div class="process-card-number"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="process-card process-card-2">
        <div class="process-card-title">Prototyping</div>
        <div class="process-card-desc">This stage involves creating a prototype or demo of the product to be developed. Feedback is gathered at this stage and changes are made as needed.</div>
        <div class="process-card-number"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="process-card process-card-3">
        <div class="process-card-title">Setting Up Your Team</div>
        <div class="process-card-desc">A dedicated, talented, and exclusive team is set up for the project. The team composition can be chosen based on budget and deadlines are established.</div>
        <div class="process-card-number"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="process-card process-card-4">
        <div class="process-card-title">Agile Software Development</div>
        <div class="process-card-desc">This approach is used to speed up the development process, ensuring that the product is sustainable, well-designed, and delivered quickly.</div>
        <div class="process-card-number"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="process-card process-card-5">
        <div class="process-card-title">Technical And Marketing Support</div>
        <div class="process-card-desc">After launch, services such as SEO, marketing, performance monitoring, and upgrades are provided to ensure the success of the product in the market.</div>
        <div class="process-card-number"></div>
    </div>
</section>

